quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  7,164,"Tuma nde dentaal jeyaa…óo e ma…ì…ìe wi'noo : "Ko hol…óum mbaajoanto…óon yim…ìe, Allaahu ko kalkoowo …ìe maa O lepta …ìe lepte sattu…óe?" …ìe mbi'i : "Ko [ittugol] ngantu faade ka Joomi mo'on ; e belejo'o, kam…ìe …ìe ndentoto"."
  7,165,"Nde …ìe njejjitunoo ko …ìe mbaajanoo fii mum kon, minn nda…óndi …ìeen ha…óaynoo…ìe e bone on, minn nanngiri …ìeen too√±u…ìe lepte sattu…óe sabu ko …ìe njalatnooko.e …óoftaare."
  7,166,"Nde …ìe townitaninoo e ko …ìe ka…óaa e mum kon, min mbi'ani …ìe : "Laatee baa…ói jaasu…ói"."
  7,167,"siftor tuma nde Joomi maa anndinnoo (won de) ma o nulu e ma…ì…ìe haa √ëalnde Darngal on mee…óinoowo …ìe lepte bon …óe. Pellet, Joomi maa ko jaawu…óe lepte, pellet kadi, ko O jaafotoo…óoo, jurmotoo…óo."
  7,168,"Men senndiri …ìe ka leydi dente : hino e ma…ì…ìe mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe, hino e ma…ì…ìe ko jaasi …óum. min njarribori …ìe mo∆¥∆¥u…ói e bo…ó…ói, mbelejo'o, kam…ìe …ìe nduttoto."
  7,169,"Lomtii …ìaawo ma…ì…ìe lomtii …ìe (bon…ìe), …ìe roni deftere nden, hi…ìe ∆¥etta wee…ìitan…óe oo aduna …ìe mbi'a : "Aray min njaaffee". Si wee…ìitannde sugu mum arii e ma…ì…ìe, …ìe ∆¥etta …óum.hara ahadi deftere nden ∆¥ettidaaka e ma…ì…ìe, won de wata …ìe wowlu e Alla si wanaa goonga?! …ìe janngi ko woni e mayre. Ko galle laakara …óen …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥annde …ìen rentii…ìe. E on kakkiltaa?!"
  7,170,"∆Åeen jogitotoo…ìe deftere nden …ìe √±ii…ìna juulde, pellet, mien min yeebataa njo…ìdi mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìeen."